product.title: Leyeet Hard Travel Case Replacement for One-Step Hair Dryer & Volumizer& Styler, EVA Carrying Case Compatible for Classic Hair Straightener Curling Irons, Only Case, Pink
product.description:
Features:
Compatible with Revlon one-step hair dryer brush/volumizer/styler.
Water-resistant hard EVA case and soft lining protect your device from shock, scratches, and dust.
Interior zippered mesh pocket for storing hairpins, barrettes, comb, or other small accessories.
Sturdy double zippers give you a better user experience for smooth opening and closing.
Strong rubber handle for easy and comfortable carrying on the go.

Specification:
Color: Grey
Material: EVA
Product size: 15.1x5.1x4.1 inches

Note:
Please allow a 1-3cm (0.4-1.18") difference due to manual measurement and slight color variation for different display settings.
Package Includes:
1 * Storage case
